{"id": "1222473992913289247", "channel_id": "1222208945519595550", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "凱刻斯：我才不在乎旺達，因為我超模的要命 （因此.. 傷痛之鰭才被削成無永久疊反擊）\n\n說實話我也覺得凱刻斯比旺達好用很多，夢引完全就是生來限制旺達強度的枷鎖\n\n旺達4算力疊200多反\n凱刻斯只要2算力", "timestamp": "2024-03-27T09:15:12.379000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "nekoinnocent", "emoji_id": "1200338279145414656", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222208945519595550", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海反擊 不掉死抗通關融災5-3", "forum_channel_id": "1181145177943982153"}
